column21: I believe that getting feedback on my HW's would have made this course way more effective for me. I understand not being able to get the full tests after turning in the HW's, but I would have liked to at least get feedback on my work and see what I missed out on.

column20: The way he presented the information in both an interactive and an easily note-takeable format, and then reviewed the last class's material at the beginning of every class, really helped me retain the knowledge, and I feel like I could confidently teach all of the material we have learned, which has not been the case for any other class ive taken
